trcache bigcache
================

This is a [trcache](https://github.com/RangelReale/trcache) wrapper for [bigcache](https://github.com/allegro/bigcache). 

## Info

| bigcache    |          |
|-------------|----------|
| Generics    | No       |
| Key types   | `string` |
| Value types | `[]byte` |



## Installation

```go
go get github.com/RangelReale/trcache/cache/bigcache
```
